
<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">

  <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-pink-100 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-pink-700">
    Built for Beauty Businesses
  </span>

  <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
    Empowering Beauty Professionals to Grow Online
  </h1>

  <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
    RemboBook is a modern booking platform that helps salons, nail technicians, barbers, spas, and other beauty professionals manage appointments, showcase their services, and accept bookings online—all from their own branded booking page.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-left text-gray-700 leading-8">

    <p>
      Every business that joins RemboBook gets its own dedicated booking space where clients can browse services, choose available time slots, and book appointments without endless phone calls or WhatsApp messages.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our goal is to simplify appointment management so beauty professionals can spend less time organizing schedules and more time serving their clients. Whether you're an independent technician or managing a growing salon, RemboBook provides the tools you need to stay organized and professional.
    </p>

    <p>
      With appointment management, client records, service management, reminders, and personalized business pages, we're building an all-in-one platform designed to help beauty businesses grow.
    </p>

    <p>
      Proudly built in Kenya, RemboBook is creating digital tools that make it easier for beauty professionals to succeed while giving clients a fast, convenient booking experience anytime, anywhere.
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
    <%= link_to "Register Your Salon",
        new_salon_registration_path,
        class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-pink-600 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-pink-600/10 hover:bg-pink-700 transition" %>

    <a
      href="https://wa.me/254711210437?text=Hi%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20RemboBook"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-green-600 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-green-700 hover:bg-green-50 transition"
